      • getQuoteRoundingLevel

        int getQuoteRoundingLevel()
        The scale at which to round BigDecimal values to during quoting and transaction calculations. In general, the scale indicates the number of places to the right of the decimal point that the number is allowed to contain. See BigDecimal for a full discussion of scale.
        Returns:
        configured value for default Quote rounding level

      • getQuoteRoundingMode

        java.math.RoundingMode getQuoteRoundingMode()
        The mode to round BigDecimal values to during quoting and transaction calculations. The default rounding mode is HALF_UP. See BigDecimal for a full discussion of mode.
        Returns:
        configured value for default Quote rounding mode
